snippet.title: Yet Another Fantasy Title - Official Developer Update Trailer | The MIX Showcase 2023
snippet.description: Take another look at Yet Another Fantasy Title and join a member of the development team for a progress update on this upcoming open-world action RPG parody game. Yet Another Fantasy Title will be available on PC.
